He believed that the principle will also have a positive impact
on the people in Taiwan. If Hong Kong continues to develop and
prosper, those in Taiwan will not be able to find excuses for not
returning to the motherland.
</P>
<P>
He said that after June 30, Hong Kong will remain his group's
financial base and the group will study how it can expand its
operation in Hong Kong in the future.  
