<HEADLINE> CPPCC Vice-Chairman Meets Armenian Visitors </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, June 16 (Xinhua) -- Wan Guoquan, vice-chairman of the
National Committee of the Chinese People's Political Consultative
Conference, met here today with Sergey G. Badalyan, deputy to the
National Assembly and first secretary of the Central Committee of
the Communist Party of Armenia, and his entourage.
</P>
<P>
Wan, who is also vice-president of the Chinese Association for
International Understanding (CAIU), exchanged views on issues of
common concern with the Armenian visitors.
</P>
<P>
The Armenian visitors are here as guests of the CAIU. Besides
Beijing, they also visited Dalian, a port city in northeast
China. 
</P>
