<HEADLINE> Myanmar Building Materials Expo'97 to Be Held </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
YANGON, June 16 (Xinhua) -- A four-day Myanmar Building
Materials, Construction Machinery and Hardware Expo'97 is due to
be opened tomorrow in Yangon, capital of Myanmar.
</P>
