<P>
He called on the company to continue buying fish from small
fishermen instead of fishing in the said areas using its own ships.
</P>
<P>
According to a report, Hellas Co. possesses fish processing
factory in Mafia, Coast Region, and fishing ship Aimilia V.
</P>
<P>
