<HEADLINE> Chinese Foreign Minister Meets Widow of Yitzhak Rabin </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, June 16 (Xinhua) -- Chinese Vice-Premier and Foreign
Minister Qian Qichen met with Mrs. Lea Rabin, widow of late
