He also expressed his admiration for Lea Rabin's consistent
support of the peace cause to which Yitzhak Rabin was dedicated
and her efforts to carry out the unfulfilled wishes of the late
Israeli statesman.
</P>
<P>
Yitzhak Rabin had attached importance to Sino-Israeli
relations, and made efforts to advance friendly and
cooperative ties between the two countries, Qian noted, "We will
not forget it."
</P>
<P>
Mrs. Lea Rabin is in Beijing to attend the opening ceremony of
a photo exhibition "Rabin Remembered," which opened here earlier
today. 
</P>
</TEXT>
