Chinese market in Shanghai, as the latest car for the 1990s in
China.
</P>
<P>
The car is produced by the Dongfeng-Citroen Automobile Co. Ltd,
a joint venture of China Dongfeng Automobile Company and France's
Citroen.
</P>
<P>
