efficient, and a speed of 180 km/per hour. The company expects to
manufacture 2,000 cars this year, with a sticker price of 160,000
yuan to 168,000 yuan.
</P>
<P>
The joint venture was started in May 1992, with headquarters in
Wuhan, capital of central China's Hubei Province. It spent 10.35
billion yuan on the first phase of construction and will have an
annual production capacity of 150,000 cars and 200,000 engines by
the end of this year. 
